{"tid":42907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【熱血時報】4個月前與大公報記者爭執　梁天琦昨日遭上門拘捕","createTime":"2016-12-17T05:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T05:58:18.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e71e6393e178438244f8a0a0ba5faaffe428e188","tid":42907,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-17-2016/34612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-17-2016%2F34612&d=L%2Bf6m%2BCTEttU5uIL0P8PbKEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=1a5596e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-17-2016/34612</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201612/12828491_10154040575654074_5528163109001843355_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201612%2F12828491_10154040575654074_5528163109001843355_o.jpg&h=09e4d044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在今年8月，網上流傳一條片段，本土民主前線發言人梁天琦被一名《大公報》記者挑釁，之後雙方發生爭執。事發4個月之後，警方昨日（12月16日）以「在公眾地方打架」罪名，上門拘捕梁天琦。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦向傳媒證實，昨日下午4時在寓所被捕，他在柴灣警署被扣留了4至5小時，進行落口供及認人手續，之後他決定「踢保」。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生於8月13日晚上，梁天琦與一名疑為《大公報》記者，在太古站發生口角，而梁天琦身穿的Tee更被扯爛。該名記者一度表示「我打工咋」、「你毛都未撚出齊」、「吹支雞大撚過你啦」。及後梁天琦拿出手機拍攝時，該記者就突然「插水」，突然高呼「嘩，梁天琦打人呀！哎呀，仲話講民主呀！講港獨嗰個梁天琦！」<br />\n<br />\n先「插水」再搶電話　疑左報記者挑釁梁天琦 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-14-2016/32161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-14-2016%2F32161&d=L%2Bf6m%2BCTEttU5uIL0P8PbKEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=8c174f4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-14-2016/32161</a>"},{"pid":"bec0a85ac200693d914623e7f6d95c4438a36424","tid":42907,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e17d7c603c36dbe51ba50abae8007b8e117cfef3","tid":42907,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci